rows.label: tev000911_MSG0010
rows.name:
At long last, a chance to settle the
score with the villain who destroyed
our beautiful Earth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0020
rows.name:
Nghhh...! I cannot contain my fury!
I say we strike now—he will burn in the
eight hot hells before the day is done![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0050
rows.name:
No time to waste, then. Move those feet!
The path to supreme enlightenment won't
carve itself![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0080
rows.name:
So you say it's not time? All right.
But you'd best believe I'm staying right
here until it is![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0090
rows.name:
Ha hah! And lo, the karmic fruit ripens!
The Buddha's guidance has led us to
this moment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0100
rows.name:
I had been contemplating challenging
Void myself, but I welcome anyone ready
to cast off their earthly desires with me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000911_MSG0110
rows.name:
Into the tiger's maw, my friends! We walk
the path of salvation—and so shall we
deliver, with our fists and with our fervor![ST:wait ]
